article_title: Happy Anniversary Obamacare Taxes, Many Happy Returns

article_metadata.description: At five years old, we can celebrate Obamacare's burdensome taxes and its promise of many more to come. Some of them don't even start until 2018.
article_metadata.author: Robert W. Wood
